-- Shortcut handling
-- Delete rows from the TEMP_ODH008
1 online task
start online screen after validation
init TEMP file
call online task
LEAVE TASK
save entry
validation ok,so save transaction
validation not ok,so call online task
end VALIDATION
cancel answer = 'N'
cancel annswer <>'N'

possible and the temp table does not support nulls

ExpSyntax.val: InStr ({1,1},'M')<>0 AND NOT (Stat (0,'C'MODE)) AND {0,2} AND NOT ({4,7})
ViewMod (0) AND Level (0)='RM' AND NOT ({0,2}) OR {4,1} AND NOT ({0,2})
NOT (GetParam ('ERROR')) OR GetParam ('ERROR') AND GetParam ('ERROR_NR')=7 AND SetParam ('ERROR','FALSE'LOG)
VarMod ('{0,25}'VAR) OR VarMod ('{0,28}'VAR) OR ({0,26}='TRUE'LOG AND ({0,27}='N' OR {0,27}='' OR ISNULL ({0,27})) OR {0,26}='FALSE'LOG AND {0,27}='Y')
VarMod ('{0,16}'VAR) OR VarMod ('{0,18}'VAR) OR VarMod ('{0,19}'VAR) OR IF ({0,10}='Y' AND {0,32} OR {0,10}='N' AND NOT ({0,32}),'FALSE'LOG,'TRUE'LOG)
